Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:52.66,Main,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:53.80,Main,,0,0,0,,这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:56.76,Main,,0,0,0,,桌布…
